column5: O.K.  We both seem to have the kitchen bug at the moment...I was supposed to make cabbage rolls, but  wifey decided to lop a chunk off the head of cabbage. So much for cabbage rolls. Instead we get cabbage casserole for supper tonight.   Tomorrow they get 3 bean chili.
Between the 2 of you.  We'll have enough gas till 2013!
I can smell the "results" from here!!
Pepe Le Peu's got nothing on me
Now you've dunnit. I think it's time I introduce you to my little friend.  You think I'm bad.   Say hello to Mongo More beans? http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BK84Ipm1zlE
Ya don't wanna be downwind from bigug in a boat either for the next 3 days after his " mystery meat chilli ".
